rows.name: Ho, there! Got any fish for me?

rows.label: qst710202_msg0101
rows.name:
That's great! Just enough to get
me started. I'll get them in my
trusty pails straight away.

rows.label: qst710202_msg0201
rows.name:
I'll need more than that
to fill all of them. Just
a few more fish please!

rows.label: qst710202_msg0202
rows.name:
I'm looking for an orange
sparkly fish in particular.
Keep an eye out for those!
